## Notification Payload Design

### APNs (iOS) Payload

```json
{
  "aps": {
    "alert": {
      "title": "Order Shipped",
      "body": "Your order #12345 is on the way."
    },
    "badge": 1,
    "sound": "default",
    "category": "ORDER_UPDATE",
    "thread-id": "order-12345",
    "mutable-content": 1
  },
  "order_id": "12345",
  "deep_link": "/orders/12345"
}
```

### FCM (Android) Payload

```json
{
  "notification": {
    "title": "Order Shipped",
    "body": "Your order #12345 is on the way."
  },
  "data": {
    "order_id": "12345",
    "deep_link": "/orders/12345"
  },
  "android": {
    "notification": {
      "channel_id": "orders",
      "click_action": "OPEN_ORDER"
    }
  }
}
```

### Payload Rules

- [ ] `data` (FCM) or custom keys (APNs) for routing; do not rely on body parsing
- [ ] Include `deep_link` or equivalent for navigation on tap
- [ ] Keep payload under 4 KB (APNs limit)
- [ ] Use `content-available: 1` for silent/background only (no alert)
- [ ] `thread-id` (iOS) for grouping related notifications

