## Channels and Categories

### Android Channels

- [ ] Create notification channel per category (orders, messages, marketing)
- [ ] User can disable channels individually in system settings
- [ ] Channel importance affects sound and heads-up
- [ ] Set channel at first use; cannot change importance after creation

```kotlin
val channel = NotificationChannel(
  "orders",
  "Order Updates",
  NotificationManager.IMPORTANCE_HIGH
).apply {
  description = "Shipping and delivery updates"
  enableVibration(true)
}
notificationManager.createNotificationChannel(channel)
```

### iOS Categories

- [ ] Register categories for actionable notifications
- [ ] Define actions (e.g., "View", "Dismiss", "Reply")
- [ ] Handle actions in `userNotificationCenter(_:didReceive:withCompletionHandler:)`
- [ ] Categories allow custom actions on lock screen and notification center

