## Rich Notifications

### iOS (Notification Service Extension)

- [ ] Use NSE to modify content (e.g., download image)
- [ ] Set `mutable-content: 1` in payload
- [ ] Complete with modified content or original within time limit (~30s)
- [ ] Handle failure gracefully (show without image)

### Android (BigPictureStyle, etc.)

- [ ] Use `BigPictureStyle` for image notifications
- [ ] Use `BigTextStyle` for long content
- [ ] Use `MessagingStyle` for conversation threads
- [ ] Images: use URL; download in app or use FCM image URL support

### Media Guidelines

- [ ] Image max 1 MB (iOS); 1 MB recommended (Android)
- [ ] Aspect ratio 2:1 or 1:1
- [ ] Fallback when image fails to load
- [ ] Do not include sensitive data in images

