## Checklist Summary

| Area | Required |
|------|----------|
| Token management | Register, refresh, remove on logout |
| Permission timing | Contextual; not first launch |
| Payload design | data/deep_link; under 4 KB |
| Channels (Android) | Per category; user-configurable |
| Categories (iOS) | For actionable notifications |
| Rich notifications | NSE/BigPicture; fallback on failure |
| Silent push | Best-effort; document limits |
| Tap handling | Route to correct screen |
